this_title: Chelsea Birkby: No More Mr Nice Chelsea
introduction: What is it to be nice and when is it time to stop? Watch the award-winning and critically acclaimed debut stand-up hour from comedian Chelsea Birkby from the comfort of wherever you are I guess. Expect pop culture, philosophy and YOUR MUM! This special is made with love as well as gratuitous c♡m jokes and is only possible thanks to friends and favours.
